{"tid":2272711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李克強赴豫考察：不搞彎道超車","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T09:17:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5c1ebed46693f79e54ae9d37d93260028c6b8d","tid":2272711,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201105/YKVYFP3T6VEPPE2F4L64SNDRO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201105%2FYKVYFP3T6VEPPE2F4L64SNDRO4%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4JMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=31828e31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201105%2FYKVYFP3T6VEPPE2F4L64SNDRO4%2F&h=59465cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201105/YKVYFP3T6VEPPE2F4L64SNDRO4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李克強赴豫考察：不搞彎道超車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EfnjN2arWzTfN4V2GHClNs1XCg8=/1224x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KK6DRJ7UUJCNJLPO3ZETMLGMYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEfnjN2arWzTfN4V2GHClNs1XCg8%3D%2F1224x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKK6DRJ7UUJCNJLPO3ZETMLGMYU.jpg&h=9cc50759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李克強在河南鄭東新區考察科技城。<br />\n<br />\n中共五中全會確立科技自立自強的國家戰略，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創新不能急於求成<br />\n<br />\n李克強周二至周三赴河南考察，其間到中原動力智能機器人公司考察。據報道，李克強在考察中表示，「機器人研發關鍵靠（演）算法，而算法關鍵靠數學」；中國有巨大的市場，「推動應用和集成創新十分必要」。他並強調，要實現真正的創新突破，就一定要在科學方面打好基礎，而數學是基礎中的基礎；創新突破不能急於求成，也不搞彎道超車，必須潛下心來，「以十年磨一劍的精神和把冷板凳坐熱的堅強意志力，踏踏實實把數學這個基礎中的基礎打牢」。<br />\n<br />\n中美科技戰已白熱化，被西方封殺的科企面臨嚴峻挑戰。華為創辦人任正非稍早曾不諱言，中國目前的科學研究狀態類似二戰前的美國，「在研究上充滿功利主義，不重視基礎研究和基礎教育」。<br />\n<br />\n除了到科企外，李克強亦探訪了河南安陽保障房。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n央視"},{"pid":"856c270ccb73adc16c7a3b07e387b29c9f43b591","tid":2272711,"uid":52881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"強哥幾時會俾人雙規<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf9552562aec768b2fca5fd83287b546fb9579f","tid":2272711,"uid":118120,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"句句都頂習近平"},{"pid":"bf4aa836582d4278e4f3e8345ffa9e108a94d4be","tid":2272711,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"856c270ccb73adc16c7a3b07e387b29c9f43b591","tid":2272711,"uid":52881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"強哥幾時會俾人雙規<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"佢應該都係等退休<br />\n<br />\n反正威脅唔到習帝"},{"pid":"1e69d8a48cf58717ce8a00bd9c4744e9025eb96d","tid":2272711,"uid":51057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"灣道炒車就有份"},{"pid":"13de1d976e6a715268b8cf581547f37ae5bafac8","tid":2272711,"uid":61954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9j4fN2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9j4fN2.gif&h=805bf0de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fff792159bb1f141b76486b0bf42c3a729b46eb","tid":2272711,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"老習應該會殺左李克強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9fGdmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9fGdmT.jpg&h=5e2fea59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習核心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21f78e576d788e7558da99eddc87d8d4387b7af","tid":2272711,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:30:01.000Z","msg":"刁：我講一句你gut一句，句句都啄住晒。我希望你收斂下，我核心嚟㗎。"},{"pid":"0b72034ab3e205f8fe39df6069980370191ab47a","tid":2272711,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike